== 效能測試 ==
根據Dailytech效能測試的網頁<ref>[http://www.dailytech.com/article.aspx?newsid=7043 DailyTech report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailytech.com/article.aspx?newsid=7043 |date=20070519121955 }}</ref>，在一些繪圖吃重的遊戲，Radeon HD 2900 XT的平均頁面速度比nVidia GeForce 8800 GTS多出10~15%。 

搭載1024[[百萬位元組|MB]] GDDR4記憶體的Radeon HD 2900 XTX ，相對的沒有比Radeon HD 2900XT更優秀的測試結果，這是根據DailyTech的測試樣品<ref>[http://www.dailytech.com/ATI+Radeon+HD+2900+XTX+Doomed+from+the+Start/article7052.htm DailyTech report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailytech.com/ATI+Radeon+HD+2900+XTX+Doomed+from+the+Start/article7052.htm |date=20070507045658 }}</ref>。另一個評論網站表示HD 2900 XT比8800 GTS 640[[MiB|MiB]]的效能更優良<ref>[http://www.anandtech.com/video/showdoc.aspx?i=2988&p=31 AnandTech: ATI Radeon HD 2900 XT: Calling a Spade a Spade]</ref>。

有關負面報導，根據權威的電腦硬體網頁[[HardOCP|HardOCP]]，R600 HD2900XT is a letdown, and puts out a lot of heat and sub-par performance given how late to market it is. Not to mention the excessive power it uses to produce questionable performance, given its tardyness to market. Competing products from Nvidia (8800GTS 320 + 640MB versions) can found considerably cheaper, and is readily available at many online E-Tailers. They are as fast or faster, and consume far less power, and put out much less heat. [H]ardOCP concentrates on real world testing,and not synthetic benchmarks (3DMark, among others) that most other sites use.<ref>[http://enthusiast.hardocp.com/article.html?art=MTM0MSwxLCxoZW50aHVzaWFzdA== HardOCP ATI Radeon HD 2900 XT review] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070516130518/http://enthusiast.hardocp.com/article.html?art=MTM0MSwxLCxoZW50aHVzaWFzdA== |date=2007-05-16 }}</ref>

